snippet.title: Half-Life: DELTA - Full Walkthrough
snippet.description:
You are technical engineer of "Delta Base" complex who was in the wrong place at the wrong time, as an experiment at the Black Mesa Research Facility resulted in a Resonance Cascade that teleported extraterrestrial beings from the world of Xen to Earth.
Full Playthough of the Half-Life Delta Mod in a Single Video with NO Deaths!
